OL,6,FJanet Daby, Minister for Children and
OL,7,FFamilies, spoke to ITV News Social
OL,8,FAffairs Correspondent Sarah Corker
OL,10,FAt the heart of Labour's plan to
OL,11,Freform children's social care is
OL,12,Fintervening early and supporting
OL,13,Ffamilies before they hit crisis point.
OL,15,FThe long-term aim is for fewer
OL,16,Fchildren to be taken into care.
OL,18,FAs of March 2024, there were 83,630
OL,19,Fchildren in care in England, a number
OL,20,Fthat has been steadily rising since
OL,21,F2008.
