OL,3,CMore early children's social care help
OL,4,Cpromised for struggling families
OL,6,FThat in turn is pushing councils to
OL,7,Ftheir financial limits and failing
OL,8,Fthose who the system is supposed to
OL,9,Fprotect.
OL,11,FThe Families First for Children
OL,12,FPathfinder scheme started in three
OL,13,Fpilot areas in 2023 and offered more
OL,14,Fearly support for families dealing
OL,15,Fwith challenges like addiction,
OL,16,Fdisabilities and mental health issues.
OL,18,FThe government is now rolling it out
OL,19,Fnationally backed by #270 million
OL,20,Fwhich is ring-fenced for child
OL,21,Fprotection.
