OL,6,FAnnouncing the expansion, social
OL,7,Fworker-turned-politician Janet Daby,
OL,8,Fnow Minister for Children and
OL,9,FFamilies, told ITV News: "We know that
OL,10,F8 in 10 families find it difficult to
OL,11,Fget the right support, so this is
OL,12,Funiversal access for people.
OL,14,F"It's about keeping families together
OL,15,Fand preventing a crisis, giving that
OL,16,Fhelp early on which improves outcomes.
