OL,6,FThe new guidance sets a clear
OL,7,Fexpectation on all councils to reform
OL,8,Ffamily support services to better
OL,9,Fprotect children from harm and
OL,10,Fintroduce a single 'front door' to
OL,11,Fsupport services in every local area.
OL,13,FLabour said spending on services for
OL,14,Ffamilies at crisis point has risen by
OL,15,F#4 billion since 2013, but investment
OL,16,Fin early preventative support which
OL,17,Fisn't statutory has plummeted by #900
OL,18,Fmillion.
