OL,6,FAcross England, resourcing has been a
OL,7,Fproblem over the last decade due to
OL,8,Fgovernment funding cuts, rising costs
OL,9,Fand low morale.
OL,11,FLatest government statistics from
OL,12,FSeptember 2024 show a 17% vacancy rate
OL,13,Fwith 7200 social worker vacancies,
OL,14,Fdown on the previous year, but still
OL,15,Fup 23% since 2017.
OL,17,FThe vast majority of vacancies in
OL,18,FEngland, 74%, were covered by agency
OL,19,Fworkers.
