OL,6,FWhen asked what "success" would look
OL,7,Flike and how it would be measured,
OL,8,FMinister Daby who has 15 years of
OL,9,Ffrontline experience in social work,
OL,10,Freeled off a long list of aims from
OL,11,F"building our foster care base,
OL,12,Fkeeping children as close as possible
OL,13,Fto their communities, supporting
OL,14,Fkinship care and less profiteering by
OL,15,Fchildren's homes".
OL,17,FWithout radical investment, those
OL,18,Fambitious plans risk falling short.
